metadata.title: Marc Joseph New York Unisex-Child Kids Girls Leather Made in Brazil Star Ankle Boot
features: Shaft measures approximately ankle from arch
Designed in New York and handcrafted by skilled artisans in Brazil
Gel heel insert, densely padded footbed & blunt arch support for optimized comfort
Sole designed for the ideal combo of flexibility & durability
Signature durable and flexible injected rubber sole with cup-sole technology for walking traction & superior comfort
description: Bringing the same classic design to kids, while offering standout durability & craftsmanship. This sandal is playfully elegant and uniquely classic. Its sleek & snug fit are designed for a secure, flattering appeal on the foot. Its modern rubber sole is super flexible and intricately stitched to the upper for enhanced durability/support; just what kids need. Offered in a variety of colors & textures, from simple to bold, casual to adventurous, this will surely be your kids new favorite shoe.
